    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Performance is anchored by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and a rigid chassis with documented subframe reinforcement. Recent comprehensive service includes a Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with surgical precision. All suspension components remain tight, offering the quintessential analog feedback characteristic of the chassis's peak era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
