    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero wear on the premium leather bolsters or touchpoints. It has been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed monthly to preserve its factory luster. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it comes with a complete, documented service history from the original dealership, ensuring every scheduled maintenance was performed precisely on time. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion. All original keys, manuals, and a clean title are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 44500.0,
