    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. I have babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in pristine shape\u2014spotless inside and out, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage its whole life. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
