    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 993-generation Carrera 2 represents the pinnacle of air-cooled engineering. Powered by the M64/21 3.6L flat-six featuring the Varioram induction system, it delivers linear power through a precise G50 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the Weissach-pioneered LSA multi-link rear suspension and factory-spec Bilstein dampers. This example boasts an impeccable service record, with zero seepage from the crankcase or valve covers. The Brembo-sourced braking system retains firm pedal feel, and the optional limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Truly a collector-grade specimen with a pristine undercarriage, original paint depth, and no recorded mechanical deviations.",
